commit.message:
pa-hpux10.h (THREAD_MODEL_SPEC): Define.

	* pa-hpux10.h (THREAD_MODEL_SPEC): Define.

	* gthr-dce.h (UNUSED): Attribute unused macro.
	(__gthread_key_dtor): Make arguments UNUSED.
	(__gthread_key_delete): Revise for compatibility with DRAFT4
	implementation.

From-SVN: r42157

+	* gthr-dce.h (UNUSED): Attribute unused macro.
+	(__gthread_key_dtor): Make arguments UNUSED.
+	(__gthread_key_delete): Revise for compatibility with DRAFT4

+
